parameters.jsCode:
let status = $node["Code"].json["status"]

const Status = {
  approved: 'Aprovado',
  chargeback: "Reembolsado",
  canceled: "Cancelado",
  billet_printed: "Boleto",
  refunded: "Reembolsado",
  waiting_payment: "Pix"
}

for(el in Status){
  status = $node["Code"].json["status"] == el ? Status[$node["Code"].json["status"]] : status
}

$input.all()[0].json.Status = status

const utm = $node["Code"].json["sck"].split('|')

$input.all()[0].json['Utm Source'] = utm[0]
$input.all()[0].json['Utm Medium'] = utm[1]
$input.all()[0].json['Utm Campaign'] = utm[2]
$input.all()[0].json['Utm Term'] = utm[4]
$input.all()[0].json['Utm Content'] = utm[3]

return $input.all()[0].json
